Bard Slang

Bardprice - The coins paid to the guild for the
            teaching/training of a new bard.
Trial -     How bards advance in levels.  A quest must
            be done for each bard level.
Mana -      Spell points.  Mana just sounds cooler.
A Mark -    A gullible/easily fooled person.
Realms of magic - On the mud.
Reading period - The time when you just become a bard
            and are reading ALL of the lore files.

